      <title>戴尔股价因业绩不佳而大幅下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-31/dells-shares-drop-sharply-after-disappointing-earnings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[戴尔科技公司周五盘前交易中大幅下跌，原因是该公司自 2022 年以来首次实现营收增长，但未能打动对该公司 AI 服务器业务寄予厚望的投资者。销售额上升，利润超出预期。彭博情报的 Woo Jin Ho 正在接受“彭博监控”采访。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-31/dells-shares-drop-sharply-after-disappointing-earnings</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 13:05:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
